metadata.description:
When you hit the **Bottom**🧜‍♀️, it's high time you got **a vehicle** to move *underwater!* ✨👌 There are so many **awesome things** to experience down there, *no need to climb the tree!* 🌊🌳 Those **Apes**🐒 shall witness the **Creat1ve F0rce**🎨 of **Fish**🐟!

**Crypt0 Submar1ne**🚢 is a collection of **C00L0Rful**🌈 Pixel Artworks by  [**HexieShares**](https://twitter.com/hexieshares), a Beginner NFT Artist. 👩‍🎨🌐 For all her fellow Music🎶, Pixel Art👾, and Video Games🎮 fans over Web3!

**Not-Your-Typical-Generative-NFT-Collection**! 🖼️✨ All the images are *hand-picked* and got *manual post-processing* to ensure *the best quality of artwork*. 🌟☝️

Don't forget to check out **Hexie's** [**Crypto Artist Confessions**](https://etherscan.io/address/0xb94cb958b4a37f9aa8d2d8ab08e1c8d227661af7) **NFT Art Collection**! 💖🗯️

*Data stored on* **Arweave**, *'cause she's a collector herself and* **cares about the assets**. 🌌 **Enjoy! <3**

`#WomenInNFTs #WomenInWeb3 #PixelArtNFTs`
